OL,3,CPlans to introduce a four-and-a-half-
OL,4,Cday school week set to be scrapped
OL,6,FProposals to introduce a four-and-a-
OL,7,Fhalf-day school week are set to be
OL,8,Fscrapped by a council in southern
OL,9,FScotland.
OL,11,FDumfries and Galloway Council were
OL,12,Fconsidering implementing four longer
OL,13,Fdays of the week in order to create a
OL,14,Fhalf day on Fridays for students and
OL,15,Fteachers.
OL,17,FWith the model in place in other parts
OL,18,Fof Scotland, the council believed it
OL,19,Fwould improve the education, wellbeing
OL,20,Fand outcomes for children and young
OL,21,Fpeople.
